===Verb===
'''to supercharge'''
# to [[increase]] the [[power]] of an [[internal combustion engine]] (either [[Otto]] or [[Diesel]] [[cycle]]) by [[compressing]] the [[inlet]] [[air]] with [[power]] extracted from the [[crankshaft]].
# to make faster, more powerful.

